room_title: Escape room "House of CARS Steampunk Mansion" by Riddles Escape Room in Myrtle Beach
room_address: 9713 N. Kings Highway Myrtle Beach, SC 29577
room_description: If you think you are on a highway or this is all about automobiles, think again! Toss out the window any perceived notions; you're already on the wrong "track." You have 60 minutes to retrieve something that can change your life forever. Can you escape with your prized belonging?
